==Swedish==
===Etymology===
From ''[[glass#Swedish|glass]]'' (ice cream) + ''[[strut]]'' (hollow cone)

===Noun===
{{sv-noun-reg-ar|glasstrut}}

#[[ice cream cone]]; [[cornet]]
